data.description: Professinal Photos Coming Tomorrow!  HOLIDAY JACKPOT! This should definitely be on the TOP of your Christmas list! This Gem in this Sought After Location of Brookwood will not Last! Immediate Occupancy on this adorable 3 bedroom, 2 full bath Rancher on a 1.08 ACRE lot! Freshly Painted, Updated Baths, Hardwood Floors, Renovated Kitchen with White Cabinetry and New LVT Flooring, Upscale Quartzite Countertops and Stainless Appliances! Add to this, a delightful Side Screened Porch, an attached carport, outdoor tool shed, and room to spread out among the neighbors! BRICK FRONT STOOP NEEDS REPAIR( brick mason not available before this listing activated), CREDIT GIVEN BY SELLER AT SETTLEMENT!
